/*! @file
 * \brief Driver program for P@(PRE)GSSVX3D example
 *
 * <pre>
 * -- Distributed SuperLU routine (version 7.0.0) --
 * Lawrence Berkeley National Lab, Georgia Institute of Technology.
 * May 10, 2019
 *
